    <h1 class="article-title">How OSINT Opened My Eyes to Cybersecurity Threats</h1>

    <p class="article-metadata">
      Published on June 8, 2023
    </p>

    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/15793934/pexels-photo-15793934/free-photo-of-horse-in-sunlit-stable-window.jpeg" class="article-image" alt="Horse in Sunlit Stable Window">

